verbose_text: These include infiltration of the NP by CD34 + eosinophil-basophil progenitor cells XREF_BIBR; increase in the local survival of eosinophils in NP tissue (which is dependent on local IL-5) XREF_BIBR; evidence for local production of GM-CSF and IL-3 XREF_BIBR; upregulation of endothelial VCAM-1 and P-selectin XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR; production of C-C chemokines in epithelium and NP fibroblasts XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR; and local production of IL-13, which might contribute to adhesion molecule expression and enhance the action of IL-5 and eotaxin in airway tissue.
